{"tid":1388994,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足 我知你地係前線好心急 但可唔可以好好揸車...","createTime":"2019-07-30T20:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:57:50.000Z","uid":665,"like":224,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ef73d6856f2d414f5da74d98b8add8f3f33483","tid":1388994,"uid":665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:07:10.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩我係天水圍發夢圍狗<br />\n然後比人顏射煙花<br />\n咁一定有人受傷啦<br />\n有位巴打就好心急咁問有冇人受傷<br />\n佢架車泊我後面 佢問完人之後就好心急開車<br />\n但又唔扭多手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果我望撚住佢銀落我條泵把.........<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0o8s6J5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0o8s6J5.png&h=3cefa5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢見我烏低身望 就停一停問我架車有冇事<br />\n咁大家自己人 唔通要你賠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有掐住春袋答冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該大家 懇請大家<br />\n遇到突發野記得冷靜<br />\n唔好好似呢位巴打咁...<br />\n人地真係唔知屌你定唔屌你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d2752d47a422dfb5f9f9b368da0bdd05bbcae8","tid":1388994,"uid":22694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2d067ff1c2c9495f11f4f2018e6bd2746d1ed6","tid":1388994,"uid":14910,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:08:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3be1673239013fc8edf4f4360d72ff7ddcbb0b24","tid":1388994,"uid":191662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:08:44.000Z","msg":"對不起謝謝你"},{"pid":"0f2409d598e085927891e22df55d98bb496c72b3","tid":1388994,"uid":665,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"2a2d067ff1c2c9495f11f4f2018e6bd2746d1ed6","tid":1388994,"uid":14910,"like